'''3-硝基苯甲酸'''是一种有机化合物，化学式为[[C7H5NO4|C<sub>7</sub>H<sub>5</sub>NO<sub>4</sub>]]，它是[[苯甲酸|苯甲酸]]苯环间位上的氢被[[硝基|硝基]]取代的产物，是[[硝基苯甲酸|硝基苯甲酸]]的[[同分异构体|同分异构体]]之一。

==制备==
3-硝基苯甲酸可由[[苯甲酸|苯甲酸]]在较低温度下的[[硝化反应|硝化反应]]制备，其副产物为2-硝基苯甲酸（20%）和4-硝基苯甲酸（1.5%）。<ref>Takao Maki, Kazuo Takeda (2002). "Benzoic Acid and Derivatives". Ullmann's Encyclopedia of Industrial Chemistry. Weinheim: Wiley-VCH. DOI: 10.1002/14356007.a03_555</ref>[[苯甲酸甲酯|苯甲酸甲酯]]硝化后水解也可得到3-硝基苯甲酸，但产率较低。<ref>Oliver Kamm and J. B. Segur. m-Nitrobenzoic Acid. ''Org. Synth.'' 1923, 3 (73).DOI: 10.15227/orgsyn.003.0073.</ref>
:[[File:3_Nitrobenzoesäure.svg|550px]]

其它制备方法还包括{{le|3-硝基苯甲醇|3-Nitrobenzyl alcohol}}<ref>Banerjee, Amalendu; Dutt, Sachchidananda; Banerjee, Gopal Chandra; Hazra, Banasri; Datta, Hasi; Banerjee, Santanu. Studies on the oxidation of aromatic aldehydes and arylmethanols by vanadate and dichromate in dilute perchloric acid. ''Indian Journal of Chemistry, Section B: Organic Chemistry Including Medicinal Chemistry'', 1990. 29B (3): 257-262. ISSN: 0376-4699.</ref>、[[3-硝基苯甲醛|3-硝基苯甲醛]]<ref>Hunsen, Mo. Carboxylic acids from primary alcohols and aldehydes by a pyridinium chlorochromate-catalyzed oxidation. ''Synthesis'', 2005, 15. 2487-2490. ISSN: 0039-7881. DOI: 10.1055/s-2005-872085</ref>或[[3-硝基甲苯|3-硝基甲苯]]<ref>Yamazaki, Shigekazu. Chromium(VI) Oxide-Catalyzed Benzylic Oxidation with Periodic Acid. ''Organic Letters'', 1999. 1 (13): 2129-2132. ISSN: 1523-7060. DOI: 10.1021/ol991175k.</ref>的氧化反应及[[:d:Q63399425|3-硝基苯甲腈]]的水解反应<ref>Meth-Cohn, Otto; Wang, Mei-Xiang. An in-depth study of the biotransformation of nitriles into amides and/or acids using Rhodococcus rhodochrous AJ270. ''Journal of the Chemical Society, Perkin Transactions 1: Organic and Bio-Organic Chemistry'', 1997. 8. 1099-1104. ISSN: 0300-922X.</ref>。

==反应==
3-硝基苯甲酸具有酸的通性，如和[[氢氧化钾|氢氧化钾]]反应，得到3-硝基苯甲酸钾。<ref>Rouhi-Saadabad, Hamed; Akhlaghinia, Batool. Facile and direct synthesis of symmetrical acid anhydrides using a newly prepared powerful and efficient mixed reagent. ''Chemical Papers'', 2015. 69 (3). 479-485. ISSN: 0366-6352. DOI: 10.1515/chempap-2015-0042.</ref>

3-硝基苯甲酸和[[氯化亚砜|氯化亚砜]]回流反应，得到3-硝基苯甲酰氯。<ref>Xu, Yiming; Liang, Pengyun; Rashid, Haroon ur; Wu, Lichuan; Xie, Peng; Wang, Haodong; Zhang, Shuyan; Wang, Lisheng; Jiang, Jun. Design, synthesis, and biological evaluation of matrine derivatives possessing piperazine moiety as antitumor agents. ''Medicinal Chemistry Research'', 2019. 28 (10): 1618-1627. ISSN: 1054-2523. DOI: 10.1007/s00044-019-02398-2.</ref>它和[[甲醇|甲醇]]在酸催化下反应，得到3-硝基苯甲酸甲酯。<ref>Zaheer, Muhammad; Zia-Ur-Rehman, Muhammad; Rahman, Salma; Ahmed, Naveed; Chaudhary, Muhammad Nawaz. Microwave assisted synthesis of biologically active 4-hydroxy-N'-(phenylcarbonyl)-2H-1,2-benzothiazine-3-carbohydrazide 1,1-dioxide derivatives. ''Journal of the Chilean Chemical Society'', 2012. 57 (4). 1492-1496. ISSN: 0717-9324. DOI: 10.4067/S0717-97072012000400031</ref>它被还原剂（如[[氢|氢]]等）还原，可以得到3-氨基苯甲酸。<ref>Rahman, Md. Taifur; Wharry, Scott; Smyth, Megan; Manyar, Haresh; Moody, Thomas S. FAST Hydrogenations as a Continuous Platform for Green Aromatic Nitroreductions. ''Synlett'', 2020. 31 (6). 581-586. ISSN: 0936-5214. DOI: 10.1055/s-0037-1610751.</ref>

